 더 어렵지 않아!?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"나나미","body":"그, 그렇구나!\n뭐 우연일지도 모르니까!\n다음엔 안 그러지 않을까~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"토우코","body":"음~ 자 우리 중에 공부를 잘하는 사람은\n역시 야시오랑…… 일단 후타바 정도인가.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":29}],"windowDisplayName":"츠쿠시","body":"일단이라고 붙이지 마!\n이번 시험은 어쩌다가 좀 안 좋았던 거뿐이니까!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":29,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":29,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"마시로","body":"아하하……\n야시오 씨는 낙제점 받을 일 없을 것 같아.\n중학교 때부터 계속 학년 1등이었다고 들었어……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"루이","body":"나는 1등 할 생각으로 시험을 치르니까.\n이후로도 그럴 예정이야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":29}],"windowDisplayName":"츠쿠시","body":"받을 작정이라니\n진짜 계속 받고 있다는 게 대단하네……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":29,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":29,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"토우코","body":"나도 한 번 정도는 엄청 좋은 점수 받고 싶다~!\n중학교 때부터 계속 뒤에서 세는 게 빠르다니까!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":29}],"windowDisplayName":"츠쿠시","body":"토우코 짱은 한 번 정도가 아니라 계속 좋은 점수를 받도록 해!\n이대로는 언젠가 진짜 낙제점 받아서\n밴드 연습에 영향이 생길 거야……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":29,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":29,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"토우코","body":"그렇지!\n그러니까 야시오 선생님, 다음 시험 때 공부 가르쳐 줘!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":900000}],"windowDisplayName":"마시로・츠쿠시・나나미","body":"!?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":28,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":900000,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"마시로","body":"(와와, 어쩌지……\n야시오 씨는 그런 거 싫어할 것 같은데……)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"루이","body":"……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":29}],"windowDisplayName":"츠쿠시","body":"(어, 어라?\n그런데 의외로 진지하게 생각하는 것 같아.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":29,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":29,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"루이","body":"……그래, 상관없어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"토우코","body":"정말!?\n야시오 엄청 좋은 녀석! 신이야! 천사야! 부처님이야!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"루이","body":"사람이 좋아서 그런 게 아니야.\n네가 낙제점 받아서 밴드에 생기는 불이익과\n공부를 가르치는 코스트를 저울질해 본 거야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"나나미","body":"왠지 엄청 루이루이다운 이유……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"토우코","body":"뭐야 야시오 부끄러워하긴~!\n완전 땡큐~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"루이","body":"……어떻게 생각하든 네 자유지만.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"루이","body":"그러면 내일 이 시간까지\n문제집 27~35페이지의 문제를 전부 풀어올 것.\n알겠니?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"토우코","body":"앗, 내일부터라니 너무 급한 거 아냐!?\n다음 시험은 엄청 멀었잖아!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"루이","body":"성적을 올리고 싶다면\n우선 이해하지 못하는 부분을 없애야 하잖아?\n실제 시험 대책은 그 뒤에 해야 해.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"루이","body":"나는 어느 쪽이든 상관없지만\n중간고사 때 후회하지 않았으면 좋겠어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"episode-sr-rui-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDis